@startuml
title UC08 - Comment on Match Screen Flow
start
:Open match detail comments;
if (Logged in?) then (yes)
  :Enter comment;
  if (Valid content and not spam?) then (yes)
    :Save comment;
    :Display in comment list;
  else (no)
    :Show validation/spam message;
  endif
else (no)
  :Prompt login;
endif
stop
@enduml
